Detailed Description

cvmx_sriomaint::_pri_dev_id

Primary 8 and 16 bit Device IDs. This register defines the primary 8 and 16 bit device IDs used for large and small transport. An optional secondary set of device IDs are located in SRIOMAINT()_SEC_DEV_ID.
